It’s Go Skate Day! Learn it with my @stompsessions Trick Tip. Voted as the most “liked” on my recent post. 

Tag #stompsessions to get your Tre Flip featured on their IG stories. 

Watch all 40+ Trick Tip videos on the Stomp app. Link in their bio. 

#goskateday #skateboard #tricktip #treflip #thankyou #skateboarding #letsgo

node.text: Couldn’t be more stoked to announce the @fallen.footwear Ripper will be dropping TONIGHT at 11:59pm PST on the Fallen U.S. & EU website. We are releasing four limited colorways with a total of about 200 pairs each with more colorways coming in the fall. Thank you all for all the support so far and hope you love the Ripper as much as I do. #RiseWithTheFallen #Fallenfootwear

node.text: @fallen.footwear went to SF and skated the @thrashermag double rock park. ‘‘Twas a good time, as evidenced by the video. Learned a new trick too. Check the edit!! Link in my story

@cbdmd.usa coming in clutch. This park is our jump off park. When we go it’s always a blast. Usually the whole crew shows up and we skate far past the point of “ I should stop cause I’m gonna be hurting tomorrow”. What spot do you have like that? Lemme know cause I’m always down to try a new fun zone.

node.text: Most of a trip is talking to people. Yeah you could be skating, riding motorcycles, playing music etc. but most of your time will be spent talking. You’ll make friends and learn things. So don’t forget to practice your ability to converse with others. Also, manners never go out of style. Be polite. Haha

node.text: So, I decided to do bigger rails. About a year ago I realized that I was missing something in my skating, and although I had grinded longer rails it was probably only about two times. So I made it my business to see what I could do. On zeros trip to Florida I got this double kink back fifty with no run up. It ran in Thrasher and was shot by Kurt. My friends helped make this skateable, and cheer me on. I have a great support group of friends.
